the `copy` method isn't used anywhere and can be removed. The `readFromFile` method however is used from some tests and can be simplified. The result would look like:

```java
package org.netbeans.qa.form;

import java.io.IOException;
import java.nio.file.Files;
import java.nio.file.Paths;

public class VisualDevelopmentUtil {
    public static String JAVA_VERSION = System.getProperty("java.version");
    
